@node "hist" "StartUpChoice Documentation - History"

@{b}8. History
--- - - - -  -   -    --    -    >@{ub}

   3.00 (21.4.97) - First Public Release

   3.10 (12.1.98) - Startup little bit faster
                  - Now unused buttons disabled
                  - Now text editor can be configured (default: "C:ED")
                  - Now keeps logfile
                  - Some little fixes
                  - New docs

   3.20 (21.9.98) - Waitvalidate (Timer paused while HD is validating and then running again)
                  - Text editor doesn't have to exist anymore so you can put parameters
                    for editor now
                  - Little optimizations & bugfixes
                  - Docs now also in amigaguide format

   @{" Main " link "Main"0}

@endnode
